Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths\Nof half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma Strikes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth-based Zeon air force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One squadron has been deployed\Nfrom the Gaw attack carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Relative speed, Mach.78.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Steady as she goes.\N- Actually, its position isn't optimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it! Its approach angle is too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to do it in one try. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Standby, laser lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser sensor released! Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Looking good, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Garma, Musai capsule is on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to be burned\Nby just one Federation ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I call you Captain Garma Zabi,\Ncommander of the Earth Occupation Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me Garma, like you did\Nback at the military academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- There's the Trojan Horse there.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To think the man they call the Red Comet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...couldn't take down that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me\Nthat your time is too valuable to waste here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Think of it as a good friend\Ncoming to meet you, Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I remind you that ship made it\Nthrough the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking that as a starting point,\Nwe're calculating its fighting strength now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you've been on constant duty\Nsince the guerrilla mop-up operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get some rest.\N- I accept your kind suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However... I guarantee that they'll award you\Nthe Zeon Cross for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For giving me the opportunity\Nto prove myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here to help me\Nfinally impress my older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh. The men are watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short of spare parts in Block 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be careful with the electrical systems!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The joint hydraulics are normal.\NI'll measure the balancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- If I find even one dud, you'll be sorry!\N- Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Hayato. You sure are ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the real enemy is right in front of us.\NCan you improve in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, aren't you responsible\Nfor maintaining the tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please standby at level 1 battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't see you when we checked\Nthe bridge's monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright ordered me to look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The solution is to deploy the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to break through\Nthe Zeon lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro needs to get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike your previous battles,\Nthis time they've got all their forces in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to wait and see what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in command here!\NTake the Gundam and one Core Fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...and break through the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Knock it off, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Launch interceptor missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel, return fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let the Dopps near the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dopps coming around the stern!\NThey want to block our escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! You're ignoring orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dopps attacked before\Nthe order was executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright, I'm ready to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Sayla briefed me on the situation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you push yourself too hard,\Nyou'll just make yourself vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really think you can do it, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a question of confidence.ight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.\N- Bright! Let the Gundam go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me remind you that the Gundam\Nwasn't built for mid-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Amuro's not trained for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um, this probably won't become{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How about we use the Guntank{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- That way, It won't be as hard on Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and transfer the Gundam's\Ncockpit to the Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave two Core Fighters\Nhere for interception.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that acceptable, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we break through?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamble, continue pursuing the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger, Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Guevil squadron gets in front,\Nwe'll initiate attack. Guevil, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Guevil squadron, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank, hurry with the transfer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the enemy's attack\Nso restrained, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to take the White Base\Nwithout damaging it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Descend, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let the Zeons have this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank top portion, transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank assembly, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright, I'm awaiting your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Got It. Leave It to me.ch pad and wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceeding slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally overworked, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, when we launch from the White Base,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- We'll break up their formation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it...\NThe enemy is after the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't cover it from far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Guntank can attract their attention...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and we can split up the enemy forces...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato. You just shoot down\Nas many enemies as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you use the mountains as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance the ground forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to capture the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Altitude, 105 meters.\NWhite Base holding steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank, okay to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you are okay to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct for balance and descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Set to launch!\NReady, Hayato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's that?! Looks like a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which way, Hayato?!\N- Turn to the rear right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What fire power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the mountains as a shield...\Nand break through with the Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The air teams will be obstructed\Nand unable to attack so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's going on?!\N- Enemy ground forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Magella Attack tanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Retreat! Fall back! No, turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! Where are you aiming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward cannons, concentrate fire on\NMagella Attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to retreat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your first time in the White Base.\NWe have more experience than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! That's insubordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be satisfied if we break through\Nthe enemy's siege?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll take over for you.\N- We can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just have to pull this, right?\N- Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible! You're hitting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! As long as we're positioned{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the enemy will increase their sorties.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to bust open an escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! It's Bright!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do me a favor. The Guntank isn't mobiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you go in with the Gundam?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, I'm begging you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! It's just as Mr. Bright says!\NThe Magella Attack tanks are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's easier to fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have Kai or Ms. Sayla\Npilot the Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ms. Sayla can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing but fish in a barrel here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need to split their fighting strength{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A report, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have information that the tank\Nis a new type of mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a mobile suit? I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the Federation's new mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Its firepower is far above\Nthat of a conventional tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fight mobile suits with mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- We should have three.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Send instructions to the siege forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If the enemy makes it to the sea,\Nthey may escape to Federation airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them from advancing any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Understood?!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't have time to transfer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must run, Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you really taking it?\N- I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Drink this. It's a nutrition drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all I can do for you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryu, If you're not feeling confident, It's okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no choice. Launching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm doing this\Nbecause I'm overly confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, did you say something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Gundam, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't rush Into battle.k's been launched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting... It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Garma is having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's demonstrating why we twice failed\Nto capture the Federation secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's more, he has more\Nfighting strength than we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Dozle will recognize that\Nthe failure was not due to my shortcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is Garma piloting a mobile suit?\N- No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Garma chose not to suit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He could die in battle against the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, I could step in and save his hide.\NThat had been my plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank is in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm to be in front of the Guntank...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...then I have to get away from\Nthe White Base like Hayato said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gundam! Amuro!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time to launch.Zakus out there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't ask a woman how we should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Bright had been clear at the outset...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, fall back! The Gundam will get the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Hayato's a sitting duck right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's mobile suit has a beam rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What ferocious power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to get me! No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Divide the enemy's attention!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're returning to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw the enemy's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the ship and the mobile suit intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That power requires us\Nto totally reassess our war strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't let them leave this continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure I can keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them, no matter the cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. We'll have to enter the continent\Nalong the mountain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it may be Garma Zabi's domain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...there should be a Federation resistance\Nstill active in the continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we make contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright, everyone's counting on you\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's welcome our\NGundam warrior home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro! Hey!\N- Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Look at him, acting all cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam wasn't the only one fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! We baked a celebration pie for you\Nas fast as we could!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought Champagne too, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's celebrate with pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers, Amuro! Cheers, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:22:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me how devastating\Nthat secret weapon is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it was Zeon Cross material.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Already thinking about your next plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I can't miss a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored to give you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it.\NHaving you is like having a hundred men.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be able to prove myself\Nto my older sister Kycilia as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Lady Kycilia your direct superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.67,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a good friend in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get all sentimental on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to make contact\Nwith Federation HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro is sent on a mission\Nto fly over enemy lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But Char seeks to nip this plan in the bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the Core Fighter transfer to the Gundam\Nand do battle against Char?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter's Escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter's Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:54.24,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:59.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:09.46,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:14.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:19.02,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:24.40,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:28.98,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.98,0:24:39.29,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
